<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/06/30/%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%96%e4%bb%8a%e7%94%9f%e5%86%8d%e7%9b%b8%e9%81%87%ef%bc%9f%e9%82%8a%e7%89%a7%e8%88%87%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e9%a6%96%e8%a6%8b%e9%9d%a2%e4%be%bf%e5%bd%a2%e5%bd%b1%e4%b8%8d%e9%9b%a2%e5%bd%b7/">前世今生再相遇？邊牧與小貓首見面便形影不離彷彿天註定！ </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/andrew-s-ouo1hbizWwo-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你相信前世今生嗎？國外一隻狗狗與貓咪相遇的故事感動無數網友，一隻名叫「Meadow」的邊境牧羊犬，牠在與一隻新加入家庭的小貓相遇後，從此便形影不離，牠們親密無間展現出令人動容的跨物種情誼，彷彿早已命中注定。 </p>



<p>原來「Meadow」的飼主為了讓三歲的愛犬不再孤單，決定帶牠到私人農場領養一隻小貓作伴，起初只是想讓牠多個玩伴，卻沒想到這次的相遇竟開啟了一段意想不到的深厚友情。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1627" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C1627&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-219539" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1152%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1152w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/louis-philippe-poitras-sJgucUmcaKE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=110%2C146&amp;ssl=1 110w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「Meadow」幾乎無視無刻都與小貓黏在一起，讓主人感慨道：可能這就是前世今生<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>自從小貓踏入家門開始，「Meadow」就顯得特別溫柔，牠們僅有在剛見面的第一天彼此互相觀察，隨後便每日形影不離，不論是吃飯、玩耍以及午睡，甚至連坐在窗邊欣賞外頭風景時也都要黏在一起。&nbsp;</p>



<p>「Meadow」與小貓仿佛早已認定彼此是家人，舉止間流露出的默契與信任令人動容，故事曝光後引起廣大網友回響，許多人紛紛感慨留言「這就是緣分」、「牠們可能上輩子真的在一起」、「好純粹的愛」、「今生再續前緣」、「根本靈魂伴侶」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/06/30/%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%96%e4%bb%8a%e7%94%9f%e5%86%8d%e7%9b%b8%e9%81%87%ef%bc%9f%e9%82%8a%e7%89%a7%e8%88%87%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e9%a6%96%e8%a6%8b%e9%9d%a2%e4%be%bf%e5%bd%a2%e5%bd%b1%e4%b8%8d%e9%9b%a2%e5%bd%b7/">前世今生再相遇？邊牧與小貓首見面便形影不離彷彿天註定！ </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
