					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1703" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C511&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1022&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1363&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 你家的狗狗也會為了貪玩而不認主人嗎？近日國外一隻金毛犬的搞笑行為引起網上熱議， &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/06/30/%e7%8e%a9%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a0%e7%9b%a1%e8%88%88%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e5%9b%9e%e5%ae%b6%ef%bc%9f%e8%b3%b4%e7%9a%ae%e9%87%91%e6%af%9b%e7%8a%ac%e8%b6%b4%e9%99%8c%e7%94%9f%e4%ba%ba%e8%85%b3%e9%82%8a%e8%a3%9d/">玩不夠盡興不想回家？賴皮金毛犬趴陌生人腳邊裝死讓主人哭笑不得 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1703" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C511&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1022&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1363&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/jeyakumaran-mayooresan-KL2A6175LSA-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>你家的狗狗也會為了貪玩而不認主人嗎？近日國外一隻金毛犬的搞笑行為引起網上熱議，這隻名叫「 Oso 」的狗狗因為捨不得離開公園，竟上演了現場投靠別人家的鬧劇，讓飼主當場哭笑不得，網友們也紛紛直呼「可以參加奧斯卡了！」。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據狗狗的飼主表示，「 Oso 」從小就是一隻性格活潑好動的黃金獵犬，牠在家裡除了吃飯和睡覺以外，大部分時間都是在盧著家人們要求大家陪著自己玩，而且每天都一定要出門散步，否則就會開始拆家以宣洩情緒和活力。&nbsp;</p>



<p>這天飼主帶著愛犬到公園散步遊玩，活潑的「 Oso 」玩得不亦樂乎，一直到數小時過後該離開時，狗狗仍感覺玩得不夠盡興，於是開始裝聾作啞，無論被主人怎麼呼喚都不為所動，似乎一點也不想結束這趟快樂的行程。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="1627" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/zach-shup-R6SdnJnLJEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C1627&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-219541" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/zach-shup-R6SdnJnLJEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/zach-shup-R6SdnJnLJEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/zach-shup-R6SdnJnLJEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1152%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1152w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/zach-shup-R6SdnJnLJEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/zach-shup-R6SdnJnLJEg-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=110%2C146&amp;ssl=1 110w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「 Oso 」每次只要玩不夠盡興不想回家時，都會一屁股黏在地上裝死不認主人<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>正當飼主還在猶豫該怎麼把牠哄回家時，「 Oso 」竟然又出了奇招，自己主動跑到一旁陌生人的腳邊，直接一屁股坐下，四腳趴地死死黏在地板上，擺出一副用寄人籬下的方式來逃避現實，這一舉動讓主人哭笑不得，也讓在場的人忍俊不禁。&nbsp;</p>



<p>事情曝光迅速引起網上熱議，也讓許多飼主感到共鳴，紛紛表示自家的狗狗對於戶外活動的熱愛完全遠超人類想像，不少人也留言笑道「一秒換主人」、「狗界影帝」、「打死都不想回家」、「我家的狗狗也是一到公園就裝死」、「說叛變就叛變」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/06/30/%e7%8e%a9%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a0%e7%9b%a1%e8%88%88%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e5%9b%9e%e5%ae%b6%ef%bc%9f%e8%b3%b4%e7%9a%ae%e9%87%91%e6%af%9b%e7%8a%ac%e8%b6%b4%e9%99%8c%e7%94%9f%e4%ba%ba%e8%85%b3%e9%82%8a%e8%a3%9d/">玩不夠盡興不想回家？賴皮金毛犬趴陌生人腳邊裝死讓主人哭笑不得 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
			</item>
